    "body": "ETH issuance is controlled by the consensus algorithm and the hard forks enabled on your private network. Ethash (PoW) issues ether per every block, Clique (PoA) does not. Burn are enabled only for network that enabled the London hard fork.\r\n\r\nGeth does not support adding custom rules, so if you need own behavior, you'll need to code that up, but we don't have the capacity to support such endeavors. ",
